 *1315442582* 5-day photo reading test, part 2
 Let's continue with the 5-day test for photoreading as we did yesterday (<a href='http://d.hatena.ne.jp/nishiohirokazu/20110907/1315358107'>Trying the 5-day test for photoreading</a>). Today's process is
 - Day 3: Preparation → Photo → Vertical reading → X reading
 It is. The declaration of purpose is the same as before: to get a rough understanding of Freud, to determine if the book contains anything useful for my life, and to make a leveraged memo to post on my blog in 5 days. 25 minutes (1 pomodoro) of photo reading and vertical reading (super reading ), I looked at the list of keywords (or rather notes) and made another memo since I was so busy.
 
